    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Styles, periods, and cultures of the continent of Europe, which is in the northern hemisphere, is bounded by the Arctic Ocean, the Atlantic Ocean, and the Mediterranean Sea, and is generally considered to be delimited on the east by the Ural Mountains.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
